Package pt.ipbeja.estig.sd

Class Summary
Arrow Abstract Class Definition for different types of Arrow Information
CallArrow Class Definition for Call Method Arrow Information
Diagram Class Definition which represents Sequence Diagram Structure and Information
Gui Class Definition for the Graphic User Interface.
Image Class Definition to construct Sequence Diagram Image from JAVA SWING API.
Invoke Invoke a defined class method directly
ObjectData Class Definition for the Object Information.
ReturnArrow Class Definition for Return Method Arrow Information
SD Main Class for construction of Sequence Diagram of a JAVA Application (MSC - Message Sequence Chart)
SDControl For Controlling the construction of Sequence Diagram inside the JAVA Application.
SVGHandler XML Handler to Parse SVG XML format, modify and save it again
TraceFile This Class creates a Sequence Diagram from a simple Trace File for easily make a diagram without code (possibility of using a simple trace file generated from any source)
TraceSource Abstract Class to get program trace information from different sources
XMLLoader XML Handler to Parse XML document and Load the Sequence Diagram Structure.
